<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ffa2aff912c4d2f1402ca9554f3f385f>.
<#ffa2aff912c4d2f1402ca9554f3f385f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/0757b95c-829b-43da-8864-6cee947c93ce>;
