<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c3c2795b95dba31bedde9d08745d3a6d>.
<#c3c2795b95dba31bedde9d08745d3a6d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2cb9200d-57a3-4068-8157-5706fd0c587b>;
