    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2026-05-11"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "1970-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>, <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9c6a50fb-d491-48d2-b94e-d9b43f29470d> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/klimatolog_smhi.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-view.smhi.se/met-obs/ACMF.temperatur_manad_medel_view/wms?service=wms&request=getcapabilities>, <https://opendata-download-metobs.smhi.se/api/inspire/metobs-22.atom>, <https://opendata.smhi.se/metobs/api>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/hitta-data-for-en-plats/ladda-ner-vaderobservationer/airTemperatureMeanMonth>, <https://opendata-download-metobs.smhi.se/api/version/latest/parameter/22.json>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2015-09-02"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
