<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0881b4b2b7d2ad4d880cd6363deb43a7>.
<#0881b4b2b7d2ad4d880cd6363deb43a7> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d64c3388-6be6-48e4-84ef-c0586016869f>;
