<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d70a7b501adf3487f6223fcc4b9023ec>.
<#d70a7b501adf3487f6223fcc4b9023ec> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d8ec2980-752c-11ed-a51b-432755aaeed3>;
