<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#dd97d4b9896cc86b0ab82d71973f0d8b>.
<#dd97d4b9896cc86b0ab82d71973f0d8b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/977>;
