<https://doi.org/10.15468/KLLKYL> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Observation"@en, "Occurrence"@en, "OCCURRENCE"@en, "Nature preservation and biodiversity"@en;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/hvdCategory> <http://data.europa.eu/bna/c_dd313021>, <http://data.europa.eu/bna/c_b7f6a4f3>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__3809.
