    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/provenance> _:b0__44504.
_:b0__44504 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: Nationella emissionsdatabasen"@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N00526> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-06-09"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
