<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#6c254f422c63408475f75e14abea7831>.
<#6c254f422c63408475f75e14abea7831> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/140830ba-9850-4f01-a1a3-a7e79821a2b7/resource/caf1cee8-9af2-4a75-8fb7-f1d7cb11daeb>;
