<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/140830ba-9850-4f01-a1a3-a7e79821a2b7/resource/caf1cee8-9af2-4a75-8fb7-f1d7cb11daeb> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0>;
