<#e411f0837347dacd4d9be7f6f1fa5a14> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/c37d0a55-9be7-4984-9ce1-a6227c5b3c31/resource/98a640ba-5eea-42a4-b791-f34a22147f6d>;
