<#221a1a1225111d7ea7821df0e568efe9> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/d463475a-5dd9-4130-a97a-dc3e19f1da71/resource/8147ab89-e30f-43bc-9206-cafb0abeceac>;
